name: Tramway Histórico de Buenos Aires
description:
The fourth piece of the Baires collection inspired by places in Buenos Aires

A living tram museum, which provides tours for tourist and historical purposes in the neighborhood of Caballito. This undertaking was inaugurated on November 15, 1980 and covers a distance of 2 km. The Museum's collection is made up of rolling stock, preserving the same scheme (including the posters) that it wore when they were operational.
